# shadcn instructions

Use the latest version of Shadcn with Bun to install new components, like this command to add a button component:

```bash
bunx --bun shadcn@latest add button
```

Follow `AGENTS.md` for project rules. Use Bun for project commands, preserve the current shadcn `radix-lyra` teal theme, and use shadcn components before custom UI primitives.
